HTML-BBReverse 0.1
==================

HTML::BBReverse is a pure perl module for converting BBCode to HTML
and is able to convert the generated HTML back to BBCode.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

  none

